sc_cat_item.description:
Expansive sounds and a more natural feel
The Simmons SD350 provides a bigger-than-expected drum sound with a less-than-expected price. This full-size, 5-piece mesh-head electronic drum kit is the ideal, convenient setup for rehearsals, practice and recording. And the tension-able mesh heads capture more nuanced playing than any kit in its class. 

The sound module features 10 drum kits, 179 custom sounds and 10 songs. The 8 in. mesh heads offer real drum feel, while the quick assembly design allows for fast and easy setups and tear-downs.
